text: KORE-LP (99.1 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Entiat, Washington. The station is owned by Community Oriented Radio Endeavours. It airs a variety radio format. The station was assigned the KORE- LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on February 4, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * ORE-LP ORE-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2015 Category:2015 establishments in Washington (state) Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:Chelan County, Washington Category:Community radio stations in the United States
